title: You Know That I'll Be Back: Tootie's February 2015 Mix
description:
It's February and Tootie has been mostly laying low for a while. Well, that's only going to be the case for so long...


Lil' Bow Wow featuring Jermaine Dupri & Da Brat - You Know Me
TRU featuring Fiend & Full Blooded - Dangerous in My City
Dr. Dre featuring Eminem & Knoc-Turnal - The Watcher
Nappy Roots featuring Jazze Pha, Marcos Curiel - Awnaw (Rock Remix)
Korn - Y'All Want a Single
Slipknot - Spit It Out
Papa Roach - Thrown Away
Three Days Grace - I Hate Everything About You
3 Doors Down - Be Like That
Metallica - Turn the Page
Deep Purple - Child in Time
Beastie Boys - In 3's
Blur - Song 2
Various Artists - America, Fuck Yeah
Kenny Loggins - Danger Zone
Powerman 5000 - Relax
Sonic Mayhem - Fuck U Up!
Hardwell - Eclipse
Blasterjaxx & DBSTF featuring Ryder - Beautiful World
Super Square - Erase Me (Tootie Extended Mix)
Jennifer Paige - Crush
*NSYNC featuring Nelly - Girlfriend (The Neptunes Remix)
Garbage - Drive You Home
Mark Morrison featuring Angie Brown - Return of the Mack

All tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.
